{"id":4010,"date":"2025-06-09T10:52:22","date_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:52:22","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4010"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:52:22","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:52:22","slug":"deo-khau-trang-bi-mun","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/deo-khau-trang-bi-mun\/","title":{"rendered":"#Maskne: T\u1ea1i sao \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n? L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea1i sao<strong> \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n<\/strong>? Kh\u1ea9u trang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ec7 h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p kh\u1ecfi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n sau khi \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 maskne &#8211; s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa &#8220;mask&#8221; (kh\u1ea9u trang) v\u00e0 &#8220;acne&#8221; (m\u1ee5n). V\u1eady nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n khi \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft!<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"deo-khau-trang-co-gay-noi-mun-khong\"><\/span><b>\u0110eo kh\u1ea9u trang c\u00f3 g\u00e2y n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u1ea9u trang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ea9u trang ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea9u trang v\u1ea3i, kh\u1ea9u trang y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 kh\u1ea9u trang c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc cao c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1eebng nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4013\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4013\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4013\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-1.webp\" alt=\"\u0110eo kh\u1ea9u trang c\u00f3 g\u00e2y n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4013\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>\u0110eo kh\u1ea9u trang c\u00f3 g\u00e2y n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea9u trang y t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ecdc b\u1ee5i m\u1ecbn, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ea1t c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc si\u00eau nh\u1ecf trong kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n v\u1ec7 sinh, kh\u1ea9u trang y t\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i b\u1ecf, gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a nguy c\u01a1 l\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng v\u1ec7 sinh da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ea9u trang ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. Trong ph\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo, GSC s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n khi \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-deo-khau-trang-mat-lai-noi-mun\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea1i sao \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang m\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u1ea9u trang gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp g\u00e2y ra m\u1ee5n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n khi \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"do-am-va-nhiet-do-tang-cao-duoi-lop-khau-trang\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 t\u0103ng cao d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1edbp kh\u1ea9u trang<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, h\u01a1i th\u1edf n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i ti\u1ebft ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t ra ngo\u00e0i, khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 da t\u0103ng l\u00ean. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ton-thuong-da-do-ma-sat\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da do ma s\u00e1t<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1edbp kh\u1ea9u trang c\u1ecd x\u00e1t l\u00ean da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf v\u00f9ng m\u0169i, m\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u1eb1m. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi khu\u1ea9n x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n d\u1ec5 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4014\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4014\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4014\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-2.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da do ma s\u00e1t\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4014\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>T\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da do ma s\u00e1t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lo-chan-long-bit-tac-do-mo-hoi-va-dau-nhon\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u00edt t\u1eafc do m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang s\u1ebd t\u00edch t\u1ee5 trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en. Ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"di-ung-hoac-kich-ung-voi-chat-lieu-khau-trang\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u kh\u1ea9u trang<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ea9u trang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p, ho\u1eb7c kh\u1ea9u trang ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o, h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u00f9i, g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y da b\u1ecb m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, ng\u1ee9a r\u00e1t sau khi \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 da \u0111ang ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-deo-khau-trang-dung-cach-de-han-che-mun\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110eo kh\u1ea9u trang trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u00ed b\u00e1ch, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi khu\u1ea9n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4015\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4015\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4015\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-3.webp\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4015\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-khay-trang-phu-hop-ban-than\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9y trang ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang \u0111\u00fang lo\u1ea1i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m ma s\u00e1t. H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ecdn kh\u1ea9u trang:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: \u01afu ti\u00ean kh\u1ea9u trang c\u00f3 l\u1edbp l\u00f3t b\u1eb1ng cotton m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i. Tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0 nylon, rayon ho\u1eb7c polyester v\u00ec ch\u00fang d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u, d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n: Ch\u1ecdn kh\u1ea9u trang tho\u00e1ng kh\u00ed, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea5m h\u00fat m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: Kh\u1ea9u trang c\u1ea7n \u00f4m s\u00e1t khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadt. Tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-sach-da-ngay-sau-khi-thao-khau-trang\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da ngay sau khi th\u00e1o kh\u1ea9u trang<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang, l\u00e0n da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00ed b\u00e1ch do m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n t\u00edch t\u1ee5. V\u00ec v\u1eady, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ngay khi v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00e1c t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3812\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3812\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3812\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3812\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu da \u0111\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i, h\u00e3y r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o da s\u1ea1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-su-dung-khau-trang-vai\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang v\u1ea3i<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang v\u1ea3i, h\u00e3y gi\u1eb7t s\u1ea1ch sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi gi\u1eb7t kh\u1ea9u trang v\u1ea3i:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4016\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4016\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4016\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-4.webp\" alt=\"T\u00e1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang v\u1ea3i\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/36-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4016\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>T\u00e1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang v\u1ea3i<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9t gi\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang v\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u1ea9u trang c\u1ea7n s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 kh\u00f4. Tr\u00e1nh m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1ea9m m\u1ed1c g\u00e2y vi khu\u1ea9n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ki\u1ec3m tra d\u00e2y \u0111eo v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u kh\u1ea9u trang th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e3n ho\u1eb7c xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea5p, h\u00e3y thay m\u1edbi ngay<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n. H\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ea9u trang ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, gi\u1eef v\u1ec7 sinh t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1ea1i sao \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n? Kh\u1ea9u trang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ec7 h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p kh\u1ecfi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4017,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4010","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4010","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4010"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4010\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4019,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4010\/revisions\/4019"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4017"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4010"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4010"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4010"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}